    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 125,
      "text": "本章小结",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 126,
      "text": "前沿部分讲述了科研信息管理系统的研究背景，阐述了开发系统的理论意义和实践意义，最后画出了系统技术路线图。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 127,
      "text": "相关理论及主要技术",
      "style": "Heading 1",
      "alignment": "center",
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 128,
      "text": "B/S结构",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 129,
      "text": "B/S（Brower/Server，浏览器/服务器）模式，又称B/S结构，是Web兴起后的一种网络结构模式[10]。从经济可行性角度分析，B/S结构统一了客户端，将系统功能实现的核心部分集中到服务器上，简化了系统的开发、维护和使用，降低了…",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 7,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 130,
      "text": "Servlet和JSP",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 131,
      "text": "Servlet（Server Applet），全称Java Servlet，是用Java编写的服务器端程序。负责响应从浏览器发出的请求，并将请求通过转发技术带给JSP。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 8,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 132,
      "text": "JSP(Java Server Pages)本质上是一种Java Servlet，主要用于实现Java web应用程序的用户界面部分[13]。JSP接收请求后在浏览器上显示数据。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 133,
      "text": "从技术可行性角度分析，Servlet和JSP是当下流行的网页开发技术，开发人员具有较为成熟的开发经验，而且JSP拥有各种强大的企业级Java接口，有助于快速开发系统，降低系统的开发难度。从经济可行性角度分析，系统的开发难度降低，对开发人员…",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 134,
      "text": "MySQL数据库",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 135,
      "text": "MySQL作为关系型数据库，支持多种操作系统[14]。对比其他数据库，MySQL性能较高而且复杂程度较低，简单易用，适合非计算机专业的医院科研人员使用。从经济可行性角度分析，MySQL数据库体积小巧，安装简单，降低安装成本。从运行可行性角…",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 3,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 136,
      "text": "本章小结",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 137,
      "text": "本章主要介绍了系统的架构、开发技术以及数据库等，从各种角度阐述了使用上述架构、技术、数据库的可行性。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 138,
      "text": "系统分析",
      "style": "Heading 1",
      "alignment": "center",
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 139,
      "text": "系统功能需求",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 140,
      "text": "医院科研人员",
      "style": "Heading 3",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 141,
      "text": "医院科研人员的主要工作是上报科研成果，提交课题、成果、论文、著作、专利等科研信息，浏览已经发布的政策消息，下载相关文件，查询审核、评估结果，维护个人信息等。科研人员用例分析图如图3-1所示。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
