      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "center",
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 175,
      "text": "（4）课题评估：科研管理人员登录系统后，进入课题管理模块，点击“评估”按钮，对通过审核的课题进行评分，然后保存评分结果。课题评估顺序图如图3-8所示。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
