    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 359,
      "text": "非功能性测试",
      "style": "Heading 2",
      "alignment": null,
      "numbering": null,
      "run_count": 2,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 360,
      "text": "响应时间。经测试，在真实的系统运行过程中，系统响应快速，科研人员和科研管理人员提交事务的平均响应时间极短，低于2秒。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 8,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 361,
      "text": "安全性测试。普通用户（科研人员和科研管理人员）的基本信息都先由系统管理员录入，而且用户只能访问特定的用例或有限的数据。笔者在家中进行安全性测试，由于客观条件限制，无法对访问防火墙进行测试。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 8,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 362,
      "text": "可用性测试。经测试，系统界面友好，操作简单。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 8,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 363,
      "text": "容错性需求。系统提供容错机制来保证数据的正确输入。对各种错误操作弹出不同提示。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 8,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 364,
      "text": "兼容性测试。选择支持IE内核的各种浏览器，如IE浏览器、2345浏览器等进行测试，系统能正常运行。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
      "numbering": {
        "numId": 8,
        "ilvl": 0
      },
      "run_count": 1,
      "runs": null,
      "table_shape": null
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "index": 365,
      "text": "可维护性测试。关于更新问题，B/S架构直接升级服务器，无需用户重新下载客户端。",
      "style": "Normal",
      "alignment": "justify",
